h3#sources Which are the sources?
p
    | You only have to add the CSS, JavaScript and assets of Chico UI, and that's all!
p
    a.ch-btn.ch-btn-small(href="https://github.com/mercadolibre/chico") Download on GitHub
p
    | Make sure to add the stylesheet call into the&nbsp;
    code &lt;head&gt;
    |  tag.
pre
    | <link rel="stylesheet" href="chico-min-x.x.x.css" />
p
    | And you should add the JavaScript at bottom of page, before&nbsp;
    code &lt;/body&gt;
    |  tag close and&nbsp;
    strong after jQuery script call
    | .
pre
    | <script src="build/chico-min-x.x.x.js"></script>
